    <ul>
        <li *ngFor="let book of books; odd as isOdd"> <!--index is exported value, there are others-->
            {{book.name}} <span *ngIf="isOdd">(ODD)</span>
        </li>
    </ul>

    -> here 'odd' is an exported value. visit https://angular.dev/api/common/NgForOfContext
